title: Kicker PT250
description: Add extreme bass to your car's system with the Kicker 10" Subwoofer, PT250. With an amplified loaded enclosure and grille for extra protection, the subwoofer is simple to set up and remove. It is also extremely durable to ensure that is stands the test of time. With a RMS power rating of 100W and quick connect Molex power, the kicker subwoofer will provide your vehicle with enhanced sound performance. Nylon straps are included, which helps secure the enclosure into place even when the car is in motion. The carpeted design also allows it to match your car's interior. The kicker powered subwoofer with a built-in 100W amplifier features a remote bass control. With its unique design, the item can easily be transferred from one vehicle to the next providing you with unlimited versatility.

title: Jensen J12W 12-inch
description: The Jensen J12W 12-inch 1200 Watts Peak Power Polypropylene Subwoofer with Reinforced Stamped Steel Basket and 40oz Magnet will make the best addition to any vehicle. The Jensen subwoofer will greatly enhance any audio system with powerful and low sounding bass. The J12W is designed to work in both sealed and ported enclosures. title: Dual Electronics TBX10A
